author: DILLON MERRITT
title: DILLON MERRITT
text: i LOVE the odenton, md location, clean facilities and very friendly and helpful staff. and GREAT internet super specials!! i also like the capitol heights, md (where i live) location that i used previously, same compliments for them as well. if the capitol heights location had the same internet super special i found at odenton i wouldve went with them but i have to go where my money works more, even if its 30 miles away.
